					<p>Thanks for your comment. I&#8217;ve spoken to our engineers who tell me: </p>
<p>&#8220;We now know that the .mp3 extensions are part of an update to the TeslaCrypt malware, and we have released an updated detection of Troj/TeslaC-AQ to help with this.&#8221; </p>
<p>If you need any other assistance please contact Sophos support.</p>
